WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.333 --> 00:00:01.866
Your husband is leaving soon.

2
00:00:01.866 --> 00:00:03.266
You are not obedient

3
00:00:15.066 --> 00:00:16.200
The shopkeeper?

4
00:00:16.266 --> 00:00:19.266
Why is this good restaurant closed?

5
00:00:19.266 --> 00:00:22.300
Don't mention that my restaurant was doing well

6
00:00:22.300 --> 00:00:25.333
But a new restaurant just opened some time ago

7
00:00:25.333 --> 00:00:27.200
Took all my business away

8
00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:29.000
It's Hanhai Restaurant opposite.

9
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:31.700
The shopkeeper of Hanhai Restaurant is not as good as this

10
00:00:32.266 --> 00:00:34.533
You cash out your store for me.

11
00:00:34.533 --> 00:00:35.933
You want to buy my restaurant?

12
00:00:35.933 --> 00:00:36.966
Are you sure about that?

13
00:00:36.966 --> 00:00:38.933
But my restaurant doesn't make money

14
00:00:38.933 --> 00:00:40.133
As long as you are willing to sell it

15
00:00:40.133 --> 00:00:40.966
I'll take it.

16
00:00:40.966 --> 00:00:42.200
As for whether to make money or not?

17
00:00:42.200 --> 00:00:43.766
I naturally have a way to do it

18
00:00:43.766 --> 00:00:45.500
I see you are also an honest person

19
00:00:45.500 --> 00:00:46.733
100 taels of silver

20
00:00:46.733 --> 00:00:48.600
How about I sell you my restaurant?

21
00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:49.800
Shopkeeper Tang's

22
00:00:50.200 --> 00:00:52.666
Why don't you sell him to me at Hanhai Restaurant?

